<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CareerXplorer</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/remixicon/4.2.0/remixicon.css" integrity="sha512-OQDNdI5rpnZ0BRhhJc+btbbtnxaj+LdQFeh0V9/igiEPDiWE2fG+ZsXl0JEH+bjXKPJ3zcXqNyP4/F/NegVdZg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-SnH5WK+bZxgPHs44uWIX+LLJAJ9/2PkPKZ5QiAj6Ta86w+fsb2TkcmfRyVX3pBnMFcV7oQPJkl9QevSCWr3W6A==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/remixicon/4.2.0/remixicon.min.css" integrity="sha512-MqL4+Io386IOPMKKyplKII0pVW5e+kb+PI/I3N87G3fHIfrgNNsRpzIXEi+0MQC0sR9xZNqZqCYVcC61fL5+Vg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/HomeStyle.css">
    <style>
        *
        {
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
        }
        html,body
        {
            width:100%;
            height:100%;
            /* background-color: skyblue; */
        }
        .main
        {
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
            font-family: Gilroy;
            background-color: #ecebebc9;
        }
        .page1
        {
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100%;
            background-image: url(https://thumbnails.visme.co/62/e8/98/3b/d39b3c06ed78af525802f972446c673c-el1_6YLkaEcmS.jpg?v=2);
        }
        .page1 .nav
        {
            height: 11vh;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            background-color: #dad4d4;
        }
        .page1 .logo
        {
            height: 4vmax;
            width: 4.2vmax;
            background-color: #e6dbda;
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-family: Comfortaa;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin-left: 2%;
            margin-top: 0.7%;
        }
        .page1 .logo p
        {
            font-size: 2.1vmax;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .C
        {
            color: #0f52ba;
        }
        .X
        {
            color: #91c11b;
        }
        .page1 .nav .options
        {
            height: 100%;
            width:50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-evenly;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .page1 .nav .options button
        {
            height: 100%;
            width: 25%;
            border: none;
            background-color: transparent;
            font-size: 1.4vmax;
            font-family: Raleway;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .page1 .nav .options button a
        {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }     
        .page1 .nav .options button:hover
        {
            background-color: rgba(172, 172, 172, 0.692);
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .page1 .nav .options button i
        {
            font-size: 2vmax;
            font-weight: 200;
            margin-right: 0.5vmax;
        }
        .page1 .nav .options button img
        {
            height: 2vmax;
            width: 2vmax;
            object-fit: contain;
            margin-right: 0.5vmax;
        }
        .page1 .header
        {
            height: 89vh;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .page1 .content
        {
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
            mix-blend-mode:hard-light;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content:center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
            padding: 1% 0;
        }
        .page1 .logo-main
        {
            height: 40%;
            width: 70%;
            background-color: #dbdada;
            opacity: 2;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 7.5vmax;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: Comfortaa;
            margin-bottom: 2%;
        }
        .page1 .content .sub
        {
            height: 10%;
            font-family: Comfortaa;
            font-size: 2vmax;
            font-weight: 1000;
            color: #f8f8f8ea;
        }
        .page1 .content i
        {
            margin-top: 2%;
        }
        .page2
        {
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100%;
            background-image: url(https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRX9SumuoHRBZXl99Ga5FztgdRHhrr8E6vSPBxvUCD_XmIRCdjH);
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 2% 0;
        }
        .page2 h1
        {
            font-family: Comfortaa;
            backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
            /* color: #0f52ba; */
            height: 15vh;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2%;
            font-size: 3.5vmax;
        }
        .page2 h5
        {
            /* color: #91c11b; */
            font-family: Raleway;
            height: 85vh;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1% 3%;
            font-size: 2vmax;
            backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
        }
        .page3
        {
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .page4
        {
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .page5
        {
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .footer
        {
            height: 40vh;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main">
        <div class="page1">
            <div class="nav">
                <div class="logo">
                    <p class="C">C</p>
                    <p class="X">X</p>
                </div>
                <div class="options">
                    <button onclick="window.location.href='/careers'"><a href="/careers"><i class="ri-compass-discover-fill"></i>&nbsp;Careers</a></button>
                    <button onclick="window.location.href='/careers'"><a href="/assessment"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/11924/11924840.png" alt="">Assessment</a></button>
                    <% if (logged===false) { %>
                        <button onclick="window.location.href='/login'"><a href="/login"><i class="ri-login-box-line"></i>Login</a></button>
                        <button onclick="window.location.href='/register'"><a href="/register"><i class="ri-user-add-fill"></i>Register</a></button>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <button onclick="window.location.href='/profile/<%=umail%>'"><a href="/profile/<%=umail%>"><i class="ri-user-fill"></i>Profile</a></button>
                        <button onclick="window.location.href='/logout'"><a href="/logout"><i class="ri-logout-box-fill"></i>Logout</a></button>
                     <%}%>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="header">
                <div class="content">
                    <div class="logo-main">
                        <p class="C">Career</p>
                        <p class="X">Xplorer</p>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="sub">Your Future, Our Insights</h3>
                    <h3 class="sub">Building Careers that matter</h3>
                    <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line sub"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Search for Industries -->
        <div class="page2">
            <h1>About us</h1>
            <h5>Welcome to CareerXplorer, where we delve into the myriad opportunities that define India's professional landscape. Our platform, created by the team at Pratyagrah, is your gateway to understanding the diverse array of jobs available nationwide. We are passionate about shedding light on different career paths, offering invaluable insights to guide your professional journey.
                <br><br>
                At CareerXplorer, our mission is clear: to empower individuals with knowledge that spans industries, roles, and emerging trends. Whether you're a fresh graduate or a seasoned professional contemplating a change, we provide the resources needed to navigate today's dynamic job market effectively.
                <br><br>
                Join us at CareerXplorer and discover a wealth of information to steer your career toward success.</h5>
        </div>
        <!-- <div class="page3"></div>

        <div class="page4"></div>
 
        <div class="page5">
            
        </div>
        <div class="footer"></div> -->
    </div>
</body>
</html>